data.description: Ready for Downtown living? This is the one you have been waiting for! I hope you have your bike handy because this home is a bike ride away from the Hays St Bridge, The Pearl, and all that Downtown San Antonio has to offer! Located on almost 1/4 of an acre in the popular Dignowity Hill Historic District and on a corner lot, this beautiful home has plenty of space and a beautiful upgraded private backyard oasis that is perfect for large gatherings. The upgraded covered parking was built to protect your vehicle from the elements. Upon entering the home you will be greeted with a large open floor plan which has two living spaces that are perfect for arranging your home however you wish throughout the year! The large upgraded kitchen overlooks the living area to give it that open feel that is perfect for entertaining.  Enjoy the historic charm of high ceilings & modern floors. Design & features in all 3 bathrooms is upscale-modern and ready to greet you after a long day! A newly installed water softener and water heater show pride of ownership! Enjoy relaxed evenings on the large front porch to really get the feel that you are downtown living!
